    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos domnus
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2004" key="#Marquis/duke">Romowald</persName> summus
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> genti Langobardorum tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/3453" key="#Abbots">Zacharie</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> nostro <rs key="#Houses">casas</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3426" key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property"
                            >ad Pontecello</placeName> in quantas ibidem quod <name ref="Wadulfus"
                            >Wadulfus</name> habere visus fuit cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><rs key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> et <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                                >hortoras</rs> simul et clausuras qui post ipsas casas esset videtur
                            et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terrola</rs> vacua qui trans <rs
                                key="#Rivers">rivo</rs> esset, denique <rs key="#Mills">molino</rs>
                            et <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">valneo</rs> qui in nominato locum
                            esset invenietur, simul etia et <rs key="#Condomae">familia</rs></rs>
                        nomine <name ref="Albinus">Albino</name> cum uxorem suam nominem <name
                            ref="Candida">Candeda</name> cum filios et filias suas, <name
                            ref="Walda">Vvalda</name> cum filios et filias suas, <name ref="Maurus"
                            >Mauro</name>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">hortolano</rs> cum uxorem, filios et filias
                        suas, omnia et in omnibus in quantum iam nominato ad Pontecello Vvadulfo
                        habere visus fuit, tibi supra dicto Zacharie concessemus possedendum,
                        quatenus ab hodierna die habeas et possideas tu qui super Zacharias abbas et
                        a nullum quempia hominem nulla habeas aliquandum aliquam questionem aut
                        reprehensionem, sed perpetuis temporibus per hunc nostrum firmissimus
                        preceptum securiter et firmiter habere et possedere valeas, et quicquid
                        exinde facere volueris in tua habeas potestatem. Quod vero <rs
                            key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum concessionis</rs> ex
                        iussione nominatee potestati dictavi ego <persName
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3454">Persus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vicedominus et referendarius</rs> tibi
                            <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3480">Theodoaldo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> scribendum. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> in <rs key="#Palatium"
                            >palatio</rs> mense novembrio per indictione quinta. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p><emph>Editions</emph>: IS1 VIII, col. 610; IS2, X, col. 447; Troya, CDL III, n.
