                    (source of the text reproduced here); CDL, IV/2, n. 8, pp. 29-31. <emph>Document
                        summaries</emph>: Assemanus 1751-1753, II, p. 579; Di Meo 1795-1819, II, pp.
                    222-223; Bethmann, Holder-Egger 1878, 69 (v. Smidt 1910, p. 135); Chroust 1888,
                    n. 6; RIM, n. 234.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p>Bertolini O. 1926, n. 40.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
